        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2134649087" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6204417959202945939">Pretty fast, interesting, easy and also convoluted -at the same time- read.<br/>Liked the surreal elements of the story. The second person point of view for narration added to the magical realism and surrealism of the book also. <br/>Now I am eager to read analysis and probably mythology behind the story. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


